OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778256667
OL,3,CFirst ever Green MS as party leader
OL,4,CAnthony Slaughter wins seat
OL,6,FThe Green Party have secured their
OL,7,Ffirst ever Member of the Senedd in
OL,8,FWales.
OL,10,FParty Leader Anthony Slaughter secured
OL,11,Fa seat in Caerdydd Penarth, in what he
OL,12,Fcalled an "historic breakthrough".
OL,14,FSpeaking to ITV News he said: "This
OL,15,Fchanges everything, politics in Wales
OL,16,Fhas changed today. And, I am proud of
OL,17,Fthat change."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
