FL,463,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778256667
OL,3,CFirst ever Green MS as party leader
OL,4,CAnthony Slaughter wins seat
OL,6,FHe added: "It's the combination of so
OL,7,Fmany years of work by so many
OL,8,Fdedicated campaigners and members, but
OL,9,Fwe have caught the public mood.
OL,11,F"The public have really been
OL,12,Fresponding to what we have been saying
OL,13,Fin this election about the cost of
OL,14,Fliving crisis, the NHS, climate chaos,
OL,15,Fand it's the start of something big.
OL,17,F"I'm sure that our vote share is going
OL,18,Fto be the biggest is been across
OL,19,FWales, and I really hope we get
OL,20,Fcolleagues joining me."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/6
