CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778256667
OL,3,CFirst ever Green MS as party leader
OL,4,CAnthony Slaughter wins seat
OL,6,FCounting has begun in the 2026 Senedd
OL,7,FElection, with all 16 of Wales'
OL,8,Fconstituencies in the process of
OL,9,Fcalculating and declaring six
OL,10,Fsuccessful candidates.
OL,12,FWhile counting is still underway and
OL,13,Fresults still coming in across Wales,
OL,14,Fthe Green Party have already made
OL,15,Fhistory with the first candidate from
OL,16,Fthe party elected to form part of the
OL,17,Fnew Senedd.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
