PN,46205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1778256667
OL,3,CFirst ever Green MS as party leader
OL,4,CAnthony Slaughter wins seat
OL,6,FTo get an outright majority, a party
OL,7,Fwould need at least 49 seats overall.
OL,9,FFollowing the results, a new First
OL,10,FMinister will be chosen in the coming
OL,11,Fdays. They have to do this within 28
OL,12,Fdays of the election, so by 3 June.
OL,13,FThis may take place in the first
OL,14,Fmeeting of the new Welsh Parliament.
OL,16,FCandidates for the position are
OL,17,Fnominated by MSs - anyone can be
OL,18,Fnominated and members can put
OL,19,Fthemselves forwards.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/6
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
