OL,3,CFirst ever Green MS as party leader
OL,4,CAnthony Slaughter wins seat
OL,6,FIf multiple names are put forward,
OL,7,Fsomeone must get more votes than all
OL,8,Fof the other candidates combined to be
OL,9,Fsuccessful. If no one achieves this,
OL,10,Fthe candidate with fewest votes is
OL,11,Fdiscounted and further votes are held
OL,12,Funtil one person does receive a
OL,13,Fmajority.
OL,15,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,16,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,17,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,18,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,19,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,20,Fbelow...
